&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-1804&quot; title=&quot;Tika use no free json.org&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-1804&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-1804&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;#8211; convert json parsing to SAX in TEIParser, step 1: test (tallison: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/tika/commit/b290cd79d652741a0c8249f3860583b4169f6455&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/tika/commit/b290cd79d652741a0c8249f3860583b4169f6455&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
