                            <comment id="16059125" author="tallison@mitre.org" created="Thu, 22 Jun 2017 10:29:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I opened &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/deeplearning4j/deeplearning4j/issues/3561&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/deeplearning4j/deeplearning4j/issues/3561&lt;/a&gt; to request that they swap out json.org.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
